UML:Comment.name: Description: Unique integer value to order the properties of a class
Values: byReference,inline Default: inline Description: Determines whether the property value will be encoded inline or by reference
Values: true,false Default: false Description: If 'true', the property type will extend GML AbstractMetadataPropertyType. Else, it will extend GML AbstractMemberType.
